value.description:
About Event

​Come meet the new members who joined in December! Free breakfast and coffee for everyone :)

​Come have a bite and meet fellow members, new and old, before getting some work done at the hub. We'll have food out at 9:30am.

​RSVP so we order enough food!

​___

​​About 9Zero:  We’re a members-only community of founders, investors, scientists, and innovators accelerating climate solutions through meaningful relationships. Apply to join at www.9Zero.com

​This event is sponsored by Go
